================================================================================
Third-party components
================================================================================

This repository bundles or depends on the following third-party software. Their
licenses are reproduced with their distributions; the summary below records the
attributions required when redistributing.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
MoreRed  (vendored, packages/MoreRed_src/)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  The generative transition-state proposer used by the exploration loop.
  Source:  https://github.com/khaledkah/MoreRed
  License: MIT — Copyright (c) 2024 Khaled Kahouli
           (full text: packages/MoreRed_src/LICENSE)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
MD-ET  (dependency: `md-et`; the machine-learned force field)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  The ML force field that validates transition states and drives the PES loop.
  Installed as a Python dependency (not vendored here).
  Paper (please cite when using MD-ET): arXiv:2503.01431
  See the MD-ET repository for its license and attribution requirements; use of
  the MD-ET model and weights requires attribution to the MD-ET paper above.

